{"tid":399430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳銀行拒為海航再融資 啟德地資金鏈或斷裂","createTime":"2017-09-14T02:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T23:39:39.000Z","uid":51271,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2433f2273293c93ebc129c9c5fdd4df8871d7d95","tid":399430,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:49:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1505355939377&amp;issue=20170914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1505355939377%26issue%3D20170914&d=IHBGQprRvjfSOqcgIaUu5NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=010fafed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1505355939377&amp;issue=20170914</a><br />\n<br />\n資金背景神秘的海航系去年起連環以天價奪得啟德地皮，令市場譁然，但其發展大計或受阻，因最新有消息傳出，多間銀行拒絕為海航的啟德項目融資，相關地皮有可能被逼出售套現。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》今日引述消息人士報道，8間向海航系提供合共15億美元(約117億港元)短期過渡貸款以收購啟德地皮的銀行中，最少4間已表示拒絕為海航的啟德項目再融資。<br />\n<br />\n一般而言，地產公司在本港成功投得地皮後，會先向一間或多間銀行申請約一年期的短期貸款，以支付收購地價，其後相關銀行一般會與該地產公司再發放較長年期的貸款，以支持其建築成本及支付短期貸款的款項。<br />\n<br />\n不過，報道指，海航系將有35億元短期貸款將於今年11月到期，但相關的3間借貸銀行中，有2間已決定不再為海航提供進一步的貸款。海航系其餘就收購啟德地皮的短期貸款，亦將於明年1月、2月及6月陸續到期。<br />\n<br />\n若然海航未能覓得新資金償還上述短期貸款，相關啟德地或被逼出售套現。<br />\n<br />\n內地近期嚴查民企的海外併購，有傳海航亦是被關注的重點，早前更傳出，香港金管局更罕有向活躍於內地民企借貸的香港中資行及大型銀行，問卷點名查詢海航及萬達的信貸情况，相關銀行需匯報對兩間集團的授信總額度、未償還貸款餘額等資料。如今銀行拒絕為海航再融資，相信亦與收緊監管有關。"},{"pid":"8ab3d8b6cbeca4dc153ced85613267a44920ee48","tid":399430,"uid":63154,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:51:10.000Z","msg":"冇錢就咪撚扮大爺啦"},{"pid":"cc60096eb24e3a488f346b2d1aed4ac370baa894","tid":399430,"uid":82929,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"地產商借錢起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再賣樓還錢<br />\n巿民借錢買樓，再打工還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成件事好似好難明，但又行得好順暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開銀行真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 破產有政府包底，平時又控制到經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f5442b129f531cae7222d264e5e58522d11685","tid":399430,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:04:50.000Z","msg":"地皮呎價13000 建築成本一呎要4-5000 計埋銀行高利貸 成本價都成兩萬蚊"},{"pid":"2d38106e740d174e7894ba2d22a9dd080080633f","tid":399430,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:05:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67d5aa52dd51ebd82b27a2406fc2bef3326cc5b1","tid":399430,"uid":43173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地產商借錢起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再賣樓還錢<br />\n巿民借錢買樓，再打工還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成件事好似好難明，但又行得好順暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開銀行真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 破產有政府包底，平時又控制到經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印銀紙由零變有</blockquote><br />\n銀行由1蚊變$100"},{"pid":"67e6fe38693bf441d3ad68a8985f908086670f80","tid":399430,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"無實力嘅發展商終被市場淘汰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eff01a334590d08966a4dc9dad3266775721fea","tid":399430,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:1